BR_COMPILER_PARANOID_UNSAFE_PATH by Thomas Petazzoni.

[Waldemar: rebase on top of 2.39]
Signed-off-by: Waldemar Brodkorb <wbx@openadk.org>
[Romain: rebase on top of 2.33.1]
